analysis: The agent submitted function arguments with capitalized values ("Moderate", "Dynamic") instead of the expected lowercase ("moderate", "dynamic"), causing a mismatch and failure in argument matching for the RETA_H function call.
The agent used "Detailed" for the outputDetail parameter instead of "Summary" as required, resulting in a function call that did not match the expected parameters.

The agent included an extra unsupported argument "weatherDetail" in the FS_FAW function call, deviating from the required parameters "airportCode" and "flightNumber" only, resulting in a mismatch with the expected function call signature.

The agent omitted the required "ratingThreshold": "good" parameter in its GF_UIFG function call, failing to fully specify the user's request for Sci-Fi games with good ratings. Only the "interest" parameter was provided.
The agent passed a numeric rating value ("4.5") instead of the required categorical value ("high") for the "rating" parameter, failing to match the expected function signature.
